						<header>
						
							<a href="http://techblog.hybris.com/2014/03/28/exploring-google-glass/" title="Exploring Google Glass"></a>
							
							<div class="page-header"><h1 class="h2"><a href="http://techblog.hybris.com/2014/03/28/exploring-google-glass/" rel="bookmark" title="Exploring Google Glass">Exploring Google Glass</a></h1></div>
							
							<p class="meta">Posted <time datetime="2014-03-28" pubdate>March 28, 2014</time> by <a href="<a href="http://techblog.hybris.com/author/hansamann/" title="Posts by hansamann" rel="author">hansamann</a><span class="amp"> -</span> filed under <a href="http://techblog.hybris.com/category/android/" title="View all posts in android" rel="category tag">android</a>, <a href="http://techblog.hybris.com/category/conferences/" title="View all posts in conferences" rel="category tag">conferences</a>, <a href="http://techblog.hybris.com/category/hybris/" title="View all posts in hybris" rel="category tag">hybris</a>, <a href="http://techblog.hybris.com/category/mobile/" title="View all posts in mobile" rel="category tag">mobile</a>, <a href="http://techblog.hybris.com/category/wearables/" title="View all posts in wearables" rel="category tag">wearables</a>.</p>
						
